java.lang.Object
org.krmdemo.techlabs.core.dump.yaml.YamlTxtDumper
All Implemented Interfaces:
TreeDumper
public class YamlTxtDumper extends Object implements TreeDumper
Implementation of TreeDumper that dumps into the passed PrintStream the tree of a YAML logical structure in ANSI-Txt target format.
